Abbreviated Multidimensional Acculturation Scale

Source: R/data.R
AMAS.Rd

Abbreviated Multidimensional Acculturation Scale data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(AMAS)

Format

A data frame with 904 observations and 59 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI3, ADNI4, ADNI2, ADNIGO, ADNI1

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 21, ..., 10819

  • VISCODE character Visit code , with options: 4_init, 4_bl, 4_m12

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • VISDATE Registry EXAMDATE on matching VISCODE Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DONE character Was assessment/procedure done? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • NDREASON character If No, reason not done 1=Participant Unable for Cognitive Reasons ; 10=Not called for by protocol ; 11=Participant in a non-USA Site ; 12=Participant is not Latinx ; 2=Participant Unable for Other Reasons (Physical, auditory, etc.) ; 3=Participant/Study Partner Refused ; 7=Site Error ; 8=Other Reason ; 9=Unknown Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS1 character 1. I think of myself as being U.S. American. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS2 character 2. I feel good about being U.S. American. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS3 character 3. Being U.S. American plays an important part in my life. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS4 character 4. I feel that I am part of the U.S. American culture. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS5 character 5. I have a strong sense of being U.S. American. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS6 character 6. I am proud of being U.S. American. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS7 character 7. I think of myself as being___(a member of my culture of origin). 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS8 character 8. I feel good about being____(a member of my culture of origin). 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS9 character 9. Being___(a member of my culture of origin) plays an important part in my life. 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS10 character 10. I feel that I am part of___culture (culture of origin). 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS11 character 11. I have a strong sense of being___(culture of origin). 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS12 character 12. I am proud of being___(culture of origin). 1=Strongly disagree ; 2=Disagree somewhat ; 3=Agree somewhat ; 4=Strongly agree Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS13 character 13. at school or work 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS14 character 14. with American friends 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS15 character 15. on the phone 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS16 character 16. with strangers 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS17 character 17. in general 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS20 character 20. words in songs 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS21 character 21. in general 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS22 character 22. with family 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS23 character 23. with friends from the same country as you 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS24 character 24. on the phone 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • AMAS25 character 25. with strangers 1=Not at all ; 2=A little ; 3=Pretty well ; 4=Extremely well Decoded Value: Yes

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 71, ..., 106604

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 2, ..., 941

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DD_CRF_VERSION_LABEL character CRF Version Label , with options: v1

  • LANGUAGE_CODE character Language Code e=English Decoded Value: Yes

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
